    "description": "<strong>A new take on Tower Defense</strong><br>Combining mechanics from the beloved tower defense genre with auto battlers such as Autochess and Dota Underlords, this game features exciting gameplay, new challenges and great replay-value!<br><br><strong>Enemies and Bosses</strong><br>Defend your kingdom from hordes of monsters!<br><br><strong>Factions</strong><br>Each tower belongs to a faction, build multiple of the same faction to gain powerful buffs!<br><br><strong>Upgrade Towers</strong><br>Gather three of the same towers to upgrade it, gaining new abilities!<br><br><strong>Items and Synergies</strong><br>Create synergies and adapt your strategy with items!<br><br><strong>Gold and Interest</strong><br>Manage your economy to stay ahead of the curve!<br><br><strong>Unique, Challenging Maps</strong><br>Hand-drawn maps each with it's own strategic challenges and themes!",
